{"tid":1645461,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"吳同學冇講大話，她受性侵的地點是葵涌警署","createTime":"2019-10-11T01:44:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-11T04:58:08.000Z","uid":68738,"like":30,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"37ea804928eee86c061db28231492653c0fccb1e","tid":1645461,"uid":68738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T01:44:27.000Z","msg":"自吳同學除下面罩親身指控，警方旋即撇清無關新屋嶺，網絡亦多有質疑，筆者願為佐證協助澄清。<br />\n<br />\n早於九月初，筆者已訪問過吳同學。在兩小時的訪問中，她詳細講述 831 太子站被捕者的拘押過程：<br />\n<br />\n太子站＞荔枝角站＞瑪嘉烈醫院＞葵涌警署＞新屋嶺＞保釋<br />\n<br />\n一個月前吳同學已向筆者清楚憶述她在葵涌警署遭性侵的詳情，筆者有錄音存案。<br />\n<br />\n在 927 的中環集會，仍然幪面的吳同學都有清楚交代，她受性侵的地點是在葵涌警署（<a href=\"http://bit.ly/35ngnh1）。\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F35ngnh1%EF%BC%89%E3%80%82&d=tgdX0zC4r3YoKKw%2Bq%2FbDqcIAfqyfHgkV2drMeooGLQQ%3D&h=424d79fb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">bit.ly/35ngnh1）。</a><br />\n<br />\n回顧她向段校長的申訴（<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2OCoPTv）：\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2OCoPTv%EF%BC%89%EF%BC%9A&d=tgdX0zC4r3YoKKw%2Bq%2FbDqcIAfqyfHgkV2drMeooGLQQ%3D&h=0a5e56e7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">bit.ly/2OCoPTv）：</a><br />\n<br />\n「你知唔知道被捕嗰一刻我哋會被警方收電話？會用粗言穢語鬧我地。<br />\n你知唔知道警方要我地去邊就去邊，入黑房就入黑房，除衫就除衫。<br />\n你知唔知道我地有人俾速龍用棍打到呢刻都要覆診？<br />\n你知唔知新屋嶺個搜身室係全黑架？<br />\n你知唔知唔止我一個受到性暴力？<br />\n其他被補人士遭受不止一名警員不分性別性侵和虐待。<br />\n你知唔知我地俾人打時，港鐵職員望住我地視而不見？<br />\n你知唔知我地係拘留過程中俾人肉隨砧板上任人魚肉？」<br />\n<br />\n她在申訴時不可能詳細交代時地，只能概述她和一眾被捕者的經歷。<br />\n<br />\n除了極少數變態，沒有人會預先拿著錄影機錄音機侵犯受害者。因此性侵的控訴從來都相當依賴受害者供詞，這是無奈亦殘酷的事實。一些受害者因創傷而記不清楚時序，不幸地由原告變被告。<br />\n<br />\n然而吳同學由始至終都沒說過她在新屋嶺遭性侵。筆者特地重聽訪問錄音，她的證詞與她在中環在中大的發言一致，沒有出入。<br />\n<br />\n筆者沒有資格對恩恩怨怨置喙。但僅論 831 被捕的遭遇，筆者從未見吳同學有誤導隱瞞說謊。<br />\n<br />\n謹此澄清。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%90%B3%E5%90%8C%E5%AD%B8%E5%86%87%E8%AC%9B%E5%A4%A7%E8%A9%B1-%E5%A5%B9%E5%8F%97%E6%80%A7%E4%BE%B5%E7%9A%84%E5%9C%B0%E9%BB%9E%E6%98%AF%E8%91%B5%E6%B6%8C%E8%AD%A6%E7%BD%B2/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%2590%25B3%25E5%2590%258C%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E5%2586%2587%25E8%25AC%259B%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E8%25A9%25B1-%25E5%25A5%25B9%25E5%258F%2597%25E6%2580%25A7%25E4%25BE%25B5%25E7%259A%2584%25E5%259C%25B0%25E9%25BB%259E%25E6%2598%25AF%25E8%2591%25B5%25E6%25B6%258C%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E7%25BD%25B2%2F&d=tgdX0zC4r3YoKKw%2Bq%2FbDqcIAfqyfHgkV2drMeooGLQQ%3D&h=4c00cb02\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%2590%25B3%25E5%2590%258C%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E5%2586%2587%25E8%25AC%259B%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E8%25A9%25B1-%25E5%25A5%25B9%25E5%258F%2597%25E6%2580%25A7%25E4%25BE%25B5%25E7%259A%2584%25E5%259C%25B0%25E9%25BB%259E%25E6%2598%25AF%25E8%2591%25B5%25E6%25B6%258C%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E7%25BD%25B2%2F&h=2da69074\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%90%B3%E5%90%8C%E5%AD%B8%E5%86%87%E8%AC%9B%E5%A4%A7%E8%A9%B1-%E5%A5%B9%E5%8F%97%E6%80%A7%E4%BE%B5%E7%9A%84%E5%9C%B0%E9%BB%9E%E6%98%AF%E8%91%B5%E6%B6%8C%E8%AD%A6%E7%BD%B2/</a>"},{"pid":"1ced2ec53e13bd29a4369a3f61a1150e124b2f10","tid":1645461,"uid":68738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T01:47:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0145f09f937a501cf33708a7bf076fb685d776dd","tid":1645461,"uid":52342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T01:49:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c8ced70b9b003e5b25fa931291221d4bd87cf507","tid":1645461,"uid":52342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T01:49:49.000Z","msg":"除左推<br />\n唔知點幫"},{"pid":"beb7f591398c476d29fb19b16fd18835ff45c73f","tid":1645461,"uid":1477,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T01:50:17.000Z","msg":"而家我地要做嘅，係感召其他受害人企出黎證明S 小姐係可信，而唔係浪費時間討論S 小姐是否可信<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1645307\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1645307</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"269d87229171fd9e729c82d1683c073608bac697","tid":1645461,"uid":46950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T01:50:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 對唔住義士"},{"pid":"c0120cd6bf0ac47bde2d45b6fde417e9f243bafb","tid":1645461,"uid":150420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T01:50:26.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28615473171e93b192c61bb204b64241121743b3","tid":1645461,"uid":236348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T01:50:47.000Z","msg":"吳同學加油，我地一定撐到底。"},{"pid":"6c0892aaf3e8504858694601419b0c35c68e7289","tid":1645461,"uid":135276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T01:51:05.000Z","msg":"地點係重點？<br />\n定有冇係重點？<br />\n<br />\n點都好，唔會搵到証據，不過搵到有藉口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"535310ed5c53a3fcfea4009bf88d37cabc3040db","tid":1645461,"uid":68738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T01:56:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9c8dac1fcc46a161b4b57126c3ab8df25c8c0d14","tid":1645461,"uid":68738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T02:06:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5305b8d3f5311119490624856a86c681dcd21b63","tid":1645461,"uid":47042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T02:09:05.000Z","msg":"啱啱佢上881晴朗接受電話訪問<br />\n已經講得好清楚<br />\n<br />\n黑警get 錯係佢哋聆聽能力低"},{"pid":"3010d4a8ca3c418b9715ca6dbd9ecce91afc9bf0","tid":1645461,"uid":301952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T02:20:23.000Z","msg":"除左<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: green;\">鶳</span><